{"tid":2213814,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"深入淺出–睡眠幫助大腦移除有害代謝物的機制","createTime":"2020-09-22T21:34:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-24T01:47:08.000Z","uid":38861,"like":67,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"0d42f01c342ba42d2fac37a6f0a5e98766f91891","tid":2213814,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T21:34:40.000Z","msg":"日照工作的時候，我們腦部的神經細胞會產生與神經退化症狀有關連的&beta;-amyloid (A&beta;)。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HVp09rw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHVp09rw.jpg&h=6e37a573&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在睡覺尤其是深層睡眠的時候，我們腦部的神經細胞會減少產生&beta;-amyloid (A&beta;)。同時間， &beta;-amyloid (A&beta;)會從腦脊髓液轉移到血液循環系統的靜脈，離開大腦。<br />\n<br />\n夜間工作而日照時間睡覺會否達到同樣效果，暫時未有人體確實數據可以證實。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uSCqA6C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuSCqA6C.jpg&h=7c22cab4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（圖2）睡覺時份，位於腦脊髓液(CSF)的&beta;-amyloid (A&beta;)透過星狀細胞(astrocyte)的協助，抵達靜脈排出腦外；<br />\n<br />\n另有研究指出（Ref1)，部份的麻醉藥亦能促成同等效果。<br />\n<br />\n淋巴系統(Lymphatic System）是排除廢物的系統，基於排除A&beta;需要透過星狀細胞的幫助，學術界把整套系統命名為Glympathic system，取其Glial Cell(神經膠質細胞）及Lymphatic System（淋巴系統）的結合，雖則整個機制並沒有淋巴系統的參與（Ref5)。<br />\n<br />\n年老以及神經退化症狀的患者，Glympathic system效率大幅減低，因此引致大量&beta;-amyloid (A&beta;)聚積在腦部。而大量A&beta;聚積在腦部的話，亦會影響睡眠的質素，形成惡性循環(Ref6)。<br />\n<br />\n對比年輕人士，年老者的腦部A&beta;水平平均高出17%。以同等年齡作比較的話，患有神經退化症人士的腦部A&beta;水平則比健康人士平均高出31%。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tnZkpZ2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtnZkpZ2.jpg&h=210ce709&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（圖3）為作進一步了解睡覺與腦部A&beta;水平的關係，有研究(Ref2)找來20名人士，分別嘗試進行連續31小時不准睡覺以及睡覺9小時兩種環境，繼而量度A&beta;水平。<br />\n<br />\n兩種測驗環境之間，測試者平均相隔15日分別進行。結果得出，不論性別歲數，通宵一晚平均將會導致5%的A&beta;上升。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZS9P2MT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZS9P2MT.jpg&h=774b64b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（圖4）另外，他們亦發現睡眠時數與A&beta;的移除有著一定程度的正面關係。而另一研究(Ref3)找來了142名試驗者，發現睡眠質素越高的話，A&beta;的移除比率亦會越大。<br />\n<br />\n只不過，亦有研究指出睡眠時數少於5小時或多於11的話，認知能力會有衰退傾向，但未知與A&beta;是否有關。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n長遠而言，通宵會導致A&beta;在腦部的聚積，增加患上神經退化症狀的機會，情況許可的話，可免就則免。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果想我快啲出文的話，請<span class=\"blue\">入去Penana網站科普專欄&ndash;薯不揀單</span>俾一個<span class=\"green\">like</span>以及<span class=\"red\">Bookmark</span>，這對我非常之重要。<br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fstory%2F66244%2F%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%2599%25AE%25E5%25B0%2588%25E6%25AC%2584-%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258F%2580%25E5%2596%25AE%2Ftoc&d=o%2BIu8jl9TkUz6xxK8T5I2zv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=f938356b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc</a><br />\n<br />\n同時亦可以在Penana網站裡按「<span class=\"gold\">買一嚿/半嚿薯仔</span>」，以課金的方式推動我繼續搜羅資料寫文，多謝。<br />\n<br />\nLink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fuser%2F27349%2F%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25BB%2594%25E8%2581%259E%25E8%258C%25B1%25E8%258E%2589%2Fportfolio&d=o%2BIu8jl9TkUz6xxK8T5I2zv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=bd3c7412\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有興趣接收科學資訊的話，歡迎follow IG: potatopigtongue。<br />\n<br />\nRef1:<a href=\"https://advances.sciencemag.org/content/5/2/eaav5447\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fadvances.sciencemag.org%2Fcontent%2F5%2F2%2Feaav5447&d=o%2BIu8jl9TkUz6xxK8T5I2zv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=d6ef97d2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://advances.sciencemag.org/content/5/2/eaav5447</a><br />\nRef2:<a href=\"https://www.pnas.org/content/115/17/4483\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pnas.org%2Fcontent%2F115%2F17%2F4483&d=o%2BIu8jl9TkUz6xxK8T5I2zv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=c0699d44\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.pnas.org/content/115/17/4483</a><br />\nRef3:<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC3676720/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC3676720%2F&d=o%2BIu8jl9TkUz6xxK8T5I2zv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=0accba8f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC3676720/</a><br />\nRef4:<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC4636982/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC4636982%2F&d=o%2BIu8jl9TkUz6xxK8T5I2zv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=70b2d2ee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC4636982/</a><br />\nRef5:<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC4636982/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC4636982%2F&d=o%2BIu8jl9TkUz6xxK8T5I2zv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=70b2d2ee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC4636982/</a><br />\nRef6:<a href=\"https://www.nature.com/articles/nrneurol.2013.269#ref-CR13\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nature.com%2Farticles%2Fnrneurol.2013.269%23ref-CR13&d=o%2BIu8jl9TkUz6xxK8T5I2zv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=e86b5308\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nature.com/articles/nrneurol.2013.269#ref-CR13</a>"},{"pid":"066372f103c98db94b9eaff6af78b6ca137f9b03","tid":2213814,"uid":49004,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T21:40:11.000Z","msg":"如果早知讀書不成<br />\n每晚瞓足精神 發育就唔只1.71<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry